walter martin a baptist 
minister known to radio listeners as the bible answer man died 
monday of a heart attack he was 60 
the program a callin talk show format was produced by the 
institute which martin founded in 1960 the show heard in 100 us 
radio markets and canada began in 1964 at a new jersey station 
martin moved the show to california in 1974 
martin was the author of books critical of some christian and 
eastern religions on grounds they were cults or had origins in 
cults one book the kingdom of the cults sold nearly 500000 
copies his latest the new age cult was published three weeks 
ago 
